{
  "stem": "26111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in regard to my sister, I still to this day haven't reached the point-- even though the chances are so minimal as to be zero-- one cannot say that beyond all doubt, she was only two years older than I-- would be only two years older than I-- that she is dead.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My parents, the same is true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, on the other hand, my father would be 111 years [LAUGHS] at this point.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother would be-- no, I mean, you know, this, this is not, not reasonable-- and, and to have escaped and to have survived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had my address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew my address-- my addresses after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew other people's address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had my address.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not out of-- if they were around, if they were alive, I would have heard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's very difficult to [SIGHS] sort of experience a, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a discrete [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] grieving period when you don't know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when everything I just said-- the situation is, is as I just said.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Grieving for the likelihood, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it isn't an absolute grieving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It isn't as absolute.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It becomes absolute as the years go by and, and you're unsuccessful in your efforts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It takes longer, obviously-- because she is much younger-- with my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I say, it's not quite terminated yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- and I have, in fact, every, every intention to, to, at some point, go to Riga after the opening up of, of that part of the world and to make inquiries.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I don't imagine that there would be any--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll try and be brief about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
